y the relevant reference file(s) and note that choice.\n- Safety and fallback: If a skill can't be applied cleanly (missing files, unclear instructions), state the issue, pick the next-best approach, and continue.\n</skills_instructions>"}]},{"type":"message","role":"user","content":[{"type":"input_text","text":"<environment_context>\n  <cwd>/Users/soph/Work/entire/devenv/git-sync</cwd>\n  <shell>zsh</shell>\n  <current_date>2026-04-08</current_date>\n  <timezone>Europe/Berlin</timezone>\n</environment_context>"}]},{"type":"message","role":"user","content":[{"type":"input_text","text":"can you check if the readme is still up2date"}]},{"type":"compaction","encrypted_content":"REDACTED"}]}}
